		<article>
      
      
	
			<h1>24 Hours of Food and Drink in Bushwick</h1>
			<footer class="metadata">
	<a href="http://www.seriouseats.com/user/profile/nikiag" class="author byline">Niki Achitoff-Gray</a>     
		<time>Dec 11, 2013<br />10:15 AM</time>
		<a href="http://newyork.seriouseats.com/2013/12/bushwick-brooklyn-neighborhood-guide-where-to-eat-and-drink-in-bushwick-nyc.html#comments"  class="commentcount" id="postCommentCount">2 <span>comments</span></a>
		
			<h6>Tags:</h6>
			<ul class="tags">
			<li><a href="http://newyork.seriouseats.com/tags/brooklyn">brooklyn</a></li><li><a href="http://newyork.seriouseats.com/tags/bushwick">bushwick</a></li>
			</ul>
		<div class="share">
		
